Package: Textpackage
Type: Package
Title: A package for text analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Silvia Strutynski
Maintainer: Silvia Strutynski <S.Strutynski@lmu.campus.de>
Description: The package is able to provide text analysis.    It's made for calculating the total number of words in a text document,    and for for generating a word cloud visualization based on the frequency    of words in a text document.Both requires a character variable or a file    path to a text file.
